posed\nframework with numerical simulations of an adaptive cruise controller for an\nautomotive system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Jun 2021 23:08:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2021 20:48:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-05"}
