ed protein\nfolding. The derived control protocols in the chaperone system closely resemble\nnatural control strategies seen in experimental measurements of heat shock\nresponse in yeast and E. coli.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jun 2021 01:41:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 21:05:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-28"}
