 for noncrossing collections, for a two parameter family of generalized\nworldsheet associahedra $\\mathcal{W}^+_{k,n}$. These specialize when $k=2$ to a\ncertain dihedrally invariant partial compactification of the configuration\nspace $M_{0,n}$ of $n$ distinct points in $\\mathbb{CP}^{1}$. Many detailed\nexamples are given throughout to motivate future work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jun 2021 02:46:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 10:53:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
